Outstanding! Great flavors with a very nice touch of lime. I added 1/2 cup Uncle Bens 5-minute rice and 1/2 cup frozen petite corn as suggested. Also, I used my hand blender to break up the huge chunks of stewed tomatoes. My husband had 3 helpings and my 2-year-old was crazy about it, too. Try it!

